In a first aspect of the present disclosure, provided is a compound of formula I, or a cis-trans isomer, an optical isomer, a racemate, a pharmaceutically acceptable salt, a prodrug, a deuterated derivative, a hydrate or a solvate thereof:

wherein in the formula I:


Z1 is selected from substituted or unsubstituted C3-C12 cycloalkylenyl, and substituted or unsubstituted 3-12 membered heterocycloalkylenyl;

Z2 is selected from a chemical bond (absent), substituted or unsubstituted C1-C6 alkylenyl, substituted or unsubstituted C2-C6 alkenylenyl, and substituted or unsubstituted C2-C6 alkynylenyl;

