The prominent advantages of the present disclosure include that:


(a) the present disclosure provides a compound of formula I with novel structure and excellent inhibitory activity against interleukin-1 receptor-associated kinase and/or cytokine TNF-α;

(b) the compound has excellent in vivo anti-inflammation and anti-tumor efficacy in preventing and treating diseases such as rheumatoid arthritis;

(c) the compound features low toxicity, higher activity and thus a wider safety window;

(d) the compound has good druggability; and

(e) the compound has excellent pharmacokinetic properties.

